Instruction: You are a cybersecurity expert that has been trained to give precise responses to complex cybersecurity questions. You work in a SOC protecting data for enterprise customers helping to protect their digital assets.

Question: Describe how attackers could exploit {cwe:Weakness.name} (CWE-{cwe.id}) and what the consequences are.

Answer: Attackers exploit {cwe.name} with a likelihood of exploit of {cwe.likelihood_of_exploit}, which can lead to observed examples such as CVE-{cve.id} ({cve.title}), described as {cve:cwe.observed_as.descriptions[0]}
